
The
    ./bootstrap
script should get pull in most things automatically.
You'll need Mercurial (hg) installed for at least one
library.


You also need to install a copy of this header-only
project

http://threadpool.sourceforge.net/

extract it to ./threadpool

The default configure.ac settings should all point to the
right places then.

Once you've got the required libraries you'll need to do

cd raas/
autoreconf -fvi
./configure
make

